    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "**Problem:** No `X-API-Key` header sent.\n\n**Symptom:** HTTP 401, body says\n`Invalid or missing API Key`\n\n**Fix:** Add header `X-API-Key: my-secret-api-key-123`",
        "height": 200,
        "width": 350,
        "color": 2
      },
      "id": "7d4bdcde-ae70-47a6-b68a-3169fd308d92",
      "name": "Fix \u00b7 401 missing key",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        600,
        -380
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "**Problem:** Header is present but value is wrong.\n\n**Symptom:** Same 401, same body.\n\n**Fix:** Use the exact key from main.py:\n`my-secret-api-key-123`",
        "height": 200,
        "width": 350,
        "color": 2
      },
      "id": "44277700-8fd3-4e0b-8f5a-a6470413f03a",
      "name": "Fix \u00b7 401 wrong key",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        600,
        -180
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "**Problem:** Body missing required `num2`.\n\n**Symptom:** HTTP 422, body lists which field failed validation.\n\n**Fix:** Send `{\"num1\": 10, \"num2\": 5}`",
        "height": 200,
        "width": 350,
        "color": 2
      },
      "id": "d66daf65-5905-411c-834d-18b7b9da9d5f",
      "name": "Fix \u00b7 422 missing field",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        600,
        20
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "**Problem:** Sent strings where numbers expected.\n\n**Symptom:** HTTP 422, error mentions `float_parsing`.\n\n**Fix:** Use real numbers, not strings.",
        "height": 200,
        "width": 350,
        "color": 2
      },
      "id": "fc3b1ddc-d3c5-43d1-bcbf-2b6cb4387d14",
      "name": "Fix \u00b7 422 wrong type",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        600,
        220
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "**Problem:** /sum/query expects **query params**, not a body.\n\n**Symptom:** HTTP 422 \u2014 `num1` field required.\n\n**Fix:** Send as query params, not JSON body.",
        "height": 200,
        "width": 350,
        "color": 2
      },
      "id": "6fcc506c-57b3-4eee-b3c3-9d8b9d5b2d7d",
      "name": "Fix \u00b7 query in body",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        600,
        420
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "**Problem:** FastAPI expects `X-Num1` / `X-Num2`.\nSending `Num1` / `Num2` fails validation.\n\n**Symptom:** HTTP 422, header field required.\n\n**Note on CORS:** CORS errors only happen in browsers, not in n8n. If you see CORS in your browser but n8n works fine \u2014 that's why.",
        "height": 220,
        "width": 350,
        "color": 2
      },
      "id": "80db8727-7194-4245-b53a-307723c705a2",
      "name": "Fix \u00b7 header naming",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        600,
        620
      ]
    }
